That all are not infected, or die not of the infection: It is not becauſe he is not able to doe it, or if he did it, it were not iuſt, and all did not deſerue it:Lament. 3.31.32.33. but becauſe the Lord will not caſt off for euer, though hee cauſe griefe: yet will he haue compaſsion according to the multitude of

 his mercies for he doth not afflict willingly;
                     Mica. 7.18 for who is a God like vnto our God, that pardoneth iniquitie, and paſſeth by the tranſgreſſion of the remnant of his heritage, he retaineth not his anger for euer, becauſe hee delighteth in mercy.
